public class SpinUp

Spins up the firing wheel, and waits for it to be on target. The LEDs are flashed quicker as it gets closer to its target speed. At the beginning, it runs the shooter full-throttle until SPEED_PID_MIN is reached, then sets the motor value to MOTORVAL_PID_MIN, then uses PID control the rest of the way.
